Invocation Name: ambient ocean waves
des:
Ambient Ocean Waves Sounds is a skill to help you improve memory, focus, and concentration by listening to the sounds of the ocean waves.

They work at the core level of the human system, DNA. The vibrations and frequencies of these powerful sounds have shown tremendous healing properties.

Just relax and feel the activation of different brain centers as you go deeper with each sound.

By default, the sound will play until you stop it. To stop the music, say "Alexa, stop.” To resume it again, say "Alexa, resume."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
